You can't go there.

561
00:31:03,720 --> 00:31:05,040
It's all their setup.

562
00:31:05,840 --> 00:31:06,680
Stop talking.

563
00:31:08,320 --> 00:31:09,580
Don't call me anymore.

564
00:31:10,240 --> 00:31:11,040
Goodbye.

565
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:14,120
Hello? Hello?

566
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:24,680
Why didn't you bring your key again?

567
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:30,320
Look how pleased you are.

568
00:31:35,080 --> 00:31:36,160
You're happy.

569
00:31:39,960 --> 00:31:42,280
Tomorrow I'm going to get the marriage certificate with Wan Xinxin.

570
00:31:42,280 --> 00:31:43,960
Now my mom can finally relax.

571
00:31:45,360 --> 00:31:46,890
Hua Ming has been detained.

572
00:31:47,040 --> 00:31:49,300
Now there's no obstacle between you two.

573
00:31:50,120 --> 00:31:52,200
This is all thanks to you.

574
00:31:53,080 --> 00:31:56,340
I just wonder if certain people, after getting remarried,

575
00:31:56,360 --> 00:31:58,040
will forget all of this.

576
00:31:58,440 --> 00:32:00,040
I won't. I'm very rational.

577
00:32:01,440 --> 00:32:02,360
It's just that

578
00:32:02,560 --> 00:32:04,640
I feel a bit sorry for Wan Xinxin.

579
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:06,360
Don't be angry.

580
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:08,880
Because she'll be taking care of my child after all.

581
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:10,800
I'm thinking that after I get the money,

582
00:32:10,800 --> 00:32:11,840
I'll give her a bit more,

583
00:32:11,840 --> 00:32:13,040
as compensation.

584
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:19,600
I knew you would be like this.

585
00:32:23,040 --> 00:32:24,760
I'm doing all this for us.

586
00:32:25,360 --> 00:32:26,560
Easy for you to say.

587
00:32:27,280 --> 00:32:28,740
Haven't I told you before?

588
00:32:28,920 --> 00:32:30,960
If you just want to be with me,

589
00:32:31,120 --> 00:32:32,680
we can get married.

590
00:32:33,640 --> 00:32:34,480
Why are you acting

591
00:32:34,480 --> 00:32:36,080
like a spoiled princess now?

592
00:32:37,160 --> 00:32:39,440
How can I be with you in my current situation?

593
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:41,560
Wouldn't that be going back to square one?

594
00:32:41,560 --> 00:32:43,160
How could it be?

595
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:46,360
I have money and a green card now.

596
00:32:46,520 --> 00:32:48,240
How could it be the same as before?

597
00:32:48,240 --> 00:32:49,720
Your money is yours.

598
00:32:49,880 --> 00:32:52,010
As for me, I'm still the same as before,

599
00:32:52,200 --> 00:32:54,730
just a minor shareholder in a car dealership.

600
00:32:55,080 --> 00:32:56,880
What do I have to keep your heart?

601
00:32:57,240 --> 00:32:58,560
After some time,

602
00:32:58,760 --> 00:33:00,560
you'll get tired of me and leave.

603
00:33:00,600 --> 00:33:03,160
You know I won't. I don't care about these things.

604
00:33:03,160 --> 00:33:04,720
But I do care.

605
00:33:05,280 --> 00:33:06,880
If I don't have my own career,

606
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:08,120
if I don't have financial stability,

607
00:33:08,120 --> 00:33:10,200
I always feel inferior in front of you.

608
00:33:10,200 --> 00:33:11,480
I feel insecure.

609
00:33:11,840 --> 00:33:14,920
How many times do I have to tell you before you understand?

610
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:15,880
Alright.

611
00:33:15,880 --> 00:33:17,810
Let's not talk about this anymore.

612
00:33:18,280 --> 00:33:19,160
You know.

613
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:21,400
You're the one I love most in my heart.

614
00:33:21,760 --> 00:33:24,400
I'm doing this so we can have

615
00:33:24,560 --> 00:33:25,560
a better life together

616
00:33:25,560 --> 00:33:27,040
without any worries.

617
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:29,800
But whenever I think about

618
00:33:29,800 --> 00:33:31,640
you two getting remarried soon,

619
00:33:32,200 --> 00:33:33,130
I feel terrible.

620
00:33:34,440 --> 00:33:36,480
Don't worry. I'll keep my promise.

621
00:35:03,920 --> 00:35:05,240
Open the door!

622
00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:08,000
Wait, how did you get up here?

623
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:10,720
Just open the door first. We'll talk after.

624
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:12,600
No way.

625
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:15,000
You think you're Spider-Man? Did you climb up here?

626
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:17,000
Listen to me. Come with me right now.

627
00:35:18,000 --> 00:35:20,040
Can you all please stop making a scene?

628
00:35:20,040 --> 00:35:22,440
The old lady will get upset again if she wakes up.

629
00:35:22,440 --> 00:35:23,480
Did Huaming send you here?

630
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:24,880
Tell him it's over between us.

631
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:26,120
When he pushed me into this situation,

632
00:35:26,120 --> 00:35:27,600
why didn't he think about the consequences?

633
00:35:27,600 --> 00:35:28,440
Fine.

634
00:35:29,640 --> 00:35:31,280
I don't care about you and Huaming.

635
00:35:31,280 --> 00:35:33,120
But I must intervene with you and Qin Gang.

636
00:35:33,120 --> 00:35:35,120
What right do you have to interfere?

637
00:35:35,200 --> 00:35:37,200
I just came from Liu Wei's place.

638
00:35:38,160 --> 00:35:39,560
I saw her with my own eyes.

639
00:35:40,040 --> 00:35:41,600
She never left.

640
00:35:43,600 --> 00:35:44,600
You don't believe me, do you?

641
00:35:44,600 --> 00:35:45,720
Come with me.

642
00:35:57,040 --> 00:35:58,320
Surprise!

643
00:35:58,560 --> 00:35:59,680
What are you doing?

644
00:35:59,680 --> 00:36:00,680
Qin Gang,

645
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:01,520
get out of my house right now!

646
00:36:01,520 --> 00:36:02,380
Don't touch me!

647
00:36:02,600 --> 00:36:03,760
I'm calling security!

648
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:05,360
Who's making all this noise?

649
00:36:06,560 --> 00:36:07,490
Thank goodness!

650
00:36:07,520 --> 00:36:08,880
I'm so glad you're here.

651
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:26,560
Xinxin, it's not what you think.

652
00:36:34,360 --> 00:36:35,620
Qin Gang, are you okay?

653
00:36:36,200 --> 00:36:37,360
Qin Gang, are you alright?

654
00:36:37,360 --> 00:36:38,160
Does it hurt?

655
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:39,520
Is it broken?

656
00:36:39,960 --> 00:36:41,440
I meant her heart.

657
00:36:43,760 --> 00:36:44,690
She deserves it.

658
00:36:46,360 --> 00:36:47,240
Xinxin.

659
00:36:49,080 --> 00:36:49,960
Are you okay?

660
00:36:51,920 --> 00:36:52,580
Be careful!

661
00:37:21,120 --> 00:37:22,600
Mom, you...

662
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:27,560
Xinxin isn't in your room.

663
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:28,960
Xinxin?

664
00:37:30,400 --> 00:37:31,260
She's not home.

665
00:37:32,080 --> 00:37:33,810
It's okay. I'll go look for her.

666
00:37:34,680 --> 00:37:36,280
She left without telling me.

667
00:37:37,080 --> 00:37:38,340
Weren't you together?

668
00:37:38,720 --> 00:37:41,050
We weren't together. I went to see Liu Wei.

669
00:37:42,720 --> 00:37:44,080
Liu Wei?

670
00:37:45,800 --> 00:37:47,840
Didn't Liu Wei go to America?

671
00:37:51,160 --> 00:37:53,080
Mom, please don't be angry.

672
00:37:53,400 --> 00:37:55,530
Please don't be upset. Let me explain.

673
00:37:56,760 --> 00:37:59,120
Liu Wei wanted to see me one last time before leaving.

674
00:37:59,120 --> 00:38:01,840
But while I was with her,

675
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:03,240
Xinxin happened to see us.

676
00:38:03,240 --> 00:38:04,480
She misunderstood the situation.

677
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:05,800
You idiot!

678
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:07,620
How could you go see her again?

679
00:38:08,120 --> 00:38:10,280
Go! Find Xinxin and bring her back!

680
00:38:10,840 --> 00:38:13,200
Don't come back if you can't find her!

681
00:38:15,280 --> 00:38:15,920
Go now!

682
00:38:16,480 --> 00:38:17,610
I'm going right now.

683
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:26,170
No, Brother Ming, something's happened.

684
00:38:26,800 --> 00:38:28,720
Why did you just come to bail me out?

685
00:38:28,720 --> 00:38:29,720
No, something happened.

686
00:38:29,720 --> 00:38:30,800
What happened?

687
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:32,920
I took Wan Xinxin to Liu Wei's place

688
00:38:33,120 --> 00:38:35,520
and caught Liu Wei with Qin Gang in the room.

689
00:38:35,600 --> 00:38:37,280
Xinxin went crazy when she saw them

690
00:38:37,280 --> 00:38:38,040
and then she ran away.

691
00:38:38,040 --> 00:38:39,240
I couldn't catch up with her.

692
00:38:39,240 --> 00:38:41,800
You're a grown man and you couldn't catch up with her?

693
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:43,280
No, I was arguing with Qin Gang

694
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:45,800
and when I turned around, she was gone.

695
00:38:47,600 --> 00:38:50,440
Do you think she might do something stupid?

696
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:51,840
She...

697
00:38:52,040 --> 00:38:53,570
What are you talking about?

698
00:38:54,200 --> 00:38:56,200
Of course she's devastated by this.

699
00:38:57,200 --> 00:39:00,000
Did you take photos with your phone like I told you?

700
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:01,600
Take photos of what?

701
00:39:01,600 --> 00:39:03,860
What do you mean what? Of those two women.

702
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:05,760
You gave me your phone.

703
00:39:05,760 --> 00:39:08,120
I thought you wanted me to call Wan Xinxin.

704
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:10,320
No, I called her many times but she didn't answer.

705
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:11,680
I went straight to her room and dragged her out.

706
00:39:11,680 --> 00:39:13,040
Okay, okay.

707
00:39:13,200 --> 00:39:14,280
Let's split up and search for her.

708
00:39:14,280 --> 00:39:14,720
Check

709
00:39:14,720 --> 00:39:16,080
any mutual friends, colleagues,

710
00:39:16,080 --> 00:39:17,940
and places she might have gone to.

711
00:39:19,240 --> 00:39:20,000
Phone.

712
00:39:20,800 --> 00:39:21,880
My phone.

713
00:39:21,880 --> 00:39:22,800
Yours, yours.

714
00:39:24,560 --> 00:39:26,040
But what am I supposed to use then?

715
00:39:26,040 --> 00:39:26,760
Buy one.

716
00:39:27,680 --> 00:39:29,440
Come on, I just paid your fine

717
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:30,920
and I'm broke now.

718
00:39:37,840 --> 00:39:39,280
Hello, I'm looking for Mr. Qin.

719
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:40,120
Okay.

720
00:39:41,120 --> 00:39:42,720
Madam, someone is here to see you.

721
00:39:42,720 --> 00:39:43,360
Thank you.

722
00:39:46,240 --> 00:39:47,970
Sorry to disturb you, Mrs. Qin.

723
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:49,520
Has Xinxin come back?

724
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:55,680
Mrs. Qin, I need to talk to Qin Gang outside.

725
00:39:58,600 --> 00:39:59,800
Come out for a moment.

726
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:22,040
You really can just sit at home like this.

727
00:40:22,040 --> 00:40:23,240
Have you looked for her?

728
00:40:23,240 --> 00:40:24,240
Of course I have.

729
00:40:24,440 --> 00:40:25,500
Where did you look?

730
00:40:25,920 --> 00:40:27,960
Why are you interrogating me like this?

731
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:30,680
Is it appropriate for you to come to our home and cause trouble now?

732
00:40:30,680 --> 00:40:33,400
Fine. This is between us.

733
00:40:33,960 --> 00:40:35,890
Let's talk about Wan Xinxin first.

734
00:40:36,640 --> 00:40:37,700
Who have you asked?

735
00:40:39,800 --> 00:40:41,400
Everyone you know, everyone I know.

736
00:40:41,400 --> 00:40:43,280
I've asked everyone we both know.

737
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:44,900
No one can find her.

738
00:40:44,920 --> 00:40:47,450
So you just gave up when you couldn't find her?

739
00:40:49,680 --> 00:40:51,240
Fine. What time did she leave?

740
00:40:51,240 --> 00:40:52,700
Around midnight, I guess.

741
00:40:53,240 --> 00:40:53,760
Okay.

742
00:40:54,520 --> 00:40:56,720
Listen carefully. Now it's between us.

743
00:40:57,160 --> 00:40:58,640
Whether I find Wan Xinxin or not,

744
00:40:58,640 --> 00:40:59,840
whenever I find her,

745
00:41:00,200 --> 00:41:01,530
I will come back for you.

746
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:11,080
Sis.

747
00:41:13,240 --> 00:41:14,120
Xuke.

748
00:41:14,120 --> 00:41:15,050
Where's Xinxin?

749
00:41:15,160 --> 00:41:16,080
She didn't come here.

750
00:41:16,080 --> 00:41:17,120
She didn't come to see you?

751
00:41:17,120 --> 00:41:17,880
No.

752
00:41:18,960 --> 00:41:20,640
What's wrong? What happened?

753
00:41:21,280 --> 00:41:23,880
She didn't come home last night.

754
00:41:24,120 --> 00:41:26,120
I've been looking for her until now.

755
00:41:26,280 --> 00:41:27,840
What should we do? Where could she have gone?

756
00:41:27,840 --> 00:41:29,280
Don't panic.

757
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:31,280
Come with me, let's search together.

758
00:41:31,280 --> 00:41:31,720
Okay.

759
00:41:31,720 --> 00:41:32,400
Is that alright?

760
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:33,600
Then I'll change my shoes.

761
00:41:33,600 --> 00:41:34,840
Alright, hurry up.

762
00:41:35,880 --> 00:41:37,880
Wan Xinxin!

763
00:41:38,080 --> 00:41:39,520
Xinxin!

764
00:41:47,280 --> 00:41:48,360
Wan Xinxin!

765
00:41:50,400 --> 00:41:51,280
Xinxin!

766
00:41:52,600 --> 00:41:53,480
Xinxin!

767
00:41:53,960 --> 00:41:54,760
Can I help you?

768
00:41:56,040 --> 00:41:58,370
I'm sorry. I mistook you for someone else.

769
00:42:08,360 --> 00:42:10,020
But it's not specific enough.

770
00:42:10,240 --> 00:42:11,960
Remember, don't be conceptual.

771
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:12,400
Be specific.

772
00:42:12,400 --> 00:42:13,400
Okay, no problem.

773
00:42:13,880 --> 00:42:15,000
Hey, Mr. Shi.

774
00:42:15,240 --> 00:42:16,000
What?

775
00:42:16,760 --> 00:42:18,290
You didn't answer my calls.

776
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:19,800
Have you seen Wan Xinxin?

777
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:21,000
Wan Xinxin?

778
00:42:21,200 --> 00:42:22,460
What is she doing here?

779
00:42:24,160 --> 00:42:25,560
Okay, I got it.

780
00:43:45,520 --> 00:43:45,840
Li!

781
00:43:47,880 --> 00:43:48,440
Jiang Qiaohua!

